<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>OKNOTOK 2025 - Your Shock Collar Portrait is Ready!</title>
</head>
<body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #000000; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;">
  <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" style="background-color: #000000;">
    <tr>
      <td align="center" style="padding: 40px 0;">
        <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="600" style="max-width: 600px;">
          <!-- Header -->
          <tr>
            <td align="center" style="padding: 20px 20px 30px 20px;">
              <h1 style="margin: 0; font-size: 36px; font-weight: bold; color: #EAB308; letter-spacing: 2px;">
                ⚡ OKNOTOK 2025 ⚡
              </h1>
              <h2 style="margin: 10px 0 0 0; font-size: 24px; color: #DC2626;">
                Your Shock Collar Portrait is Ready!
              </h2>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <!-- Main Content Box -->
          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 0 20px;">
              <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" style="border: 2px solid #DC2626; background-color: #111111; border-radius: 8px;">
                <tr>
                  <td style="padding: 40px 30px;">
                    <!-- Greeting -->
                    <p style="margin: 0 0 20px 0; font-size: 18px; color: #EAB308; font-weight: 600;">
                      Hello!
                    </p>

                    <!-- Main Message -->
                    <p style="margin: 0 0 20px 0; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #D1D5DB;">
                      Remember that afternoon when you let a stranger wrap a dog shock collar around your neck and shock you while another strange person took your portrait while yet another strange person blasted you with air?
                    </p>

                    <p style="margin: 0 0 20px 0; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #D1D5DB;">
                      If not... not sure how you ended up on this list. But if so, your portrait is ready!
                    </p>

                    <p style="margin: 0 0 30px 0; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #D1D5DB;">
                      We tried to keep the email-to-session straight but that didn't happen. So you'll have to scroll through them to find yours. Sorry about that! One day we'll have a better system. If you remember the day you were shocked, that might help.
                    </p>

                    <!-- CTA Button -->
                    <table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%">
                      <tr>
                        <td align="center" style="padding: 20px 0;">
                          <a href="<%= @heroes_url %>"
                             style="display: inline-block; padding: 16px 48px; background-color: #DC2626; color: #FFFFFF; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; border-radius: 8px; letter-spacing: 1px;">
                            BROWSE ALL PORTRAITS
                          </a>
                        </td>
                      </tr>
                    </table>

                    <!-- Alternative Link -->
                    <p style="margin: 30px 0 10px 0; font-size: 14px; color: #9CA3AF; text-align: center;">
                      Or copy and paste this link into your browser:
                    </p>
                    <p style="margin: 0 0 30px 0; font-size: 14px; word-break: break-all; text-align: center;">
                      <a href="<%= @heroes_url %>"
                         style="color: #EAB308; text-decoration: underline;">
                        <%= @heroes_url %>
                      </a>
                    </p>

                    <!-- Privacy Note -->
                    <table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%">
                      <tr>
                        <td style="background-color: rgba(234, 179, 8, 0.1); border-left: 4px solid #EAB308; padding: 15px;">
                          <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px; color: #FCD34D;">
                            <strong>Privacy Note:</strong> If after downloading you'd like your portrait removed from the app, send me the URL. There is no public gallery.
                          </p>
                        </td>
                      </tr>
                    </table>

                    <!-- Sign off -->
                    <p style="margin: 30px 0 0 0; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #D1D5DB;">
                      Thank you for trusting us with your portrait and for being part of this project!
                    </p>

                    <p style="margin: 20px 0 0 0; font-size: 16px; color: #EAB308;">
                      With electric love,<br>
                      <span style="color: #DC2626; font-weight: bold;">MR OK & the OKNOTOK Team</span>
                    </p>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <!-- Footer -->
          <tr>
            <td align="center" style="padding: 30px 20px;">
              <p style="margin: 0 0 10px 0; font-size: 12px; color: #6B7280;">
                You're receiving this because you provided your email at an OKNOTOK Shock Collar Portrait session.
              </p>
              <p style="margin: 0 0 10px 0; font-size: 12px; color: #6B7280;">
                Questions? Reply to this email or find us at camp next year!
              </p>
              <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0; font-size: 12px; color: #9CA3AF;">
                OKNOTOK • 3:00 & A • Black Rock City • Burning Man 2025
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</body>
</html>